{
  "stem": "12462.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they-- they-- they received the evidence-- that evidence in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I went on to the-- [CLEARS THROAT] the-- to von Schirach, as the gauleiter of Vienna.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a gauleiter is the main government leader of the German Reich-- of the German government-- in a particular area, called a gau, or a province.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the former country of Austria was divided up into four or five gaus.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- one was the gau Vienna, Gau Wien.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was made the gau leader of-- of Vienna, which was quite a prestigious kind of position, because-- and very important, because the Nazis were anxious to take over [CLEARS THROAT] Vienna, not merely in the sense of having occupied it, but in terms of completely weeding out any possible roots of opposition.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A lot of my proof went into the squabble that developed between the Nazi authorities and the churches, particularly of the Catholic Church, in Austria.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because [CLEARS THROAT] the churches owned a great deal of land.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the government-- the Nazi government wanted to [CLEARS THROAT] get back a lot of this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were some big, kind of, proceedings, which were loaded, of course, in terms of coming out with the churches losing some of their lands.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I introduced that evidence, as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Schirach had become quite articulate in damning some of the work of the churches.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we brought that in as a part of his [CLEARS THROAT] crimes against humanity.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you offer any testimony against the defendant?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any witnesses?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] No.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- I introduced some affidavits.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In that sense, testimony, but no witness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't call a witness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [CLEARS THROAT] basically speaking, there was not much challenge to-- by Schirach, when he took the stand.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
